			<h2><a href="/lbedgood/302486/how-data-service-daas-revolutionizing-marketing">How Data-as-a-Service (DaaS) Is Revolutionizing Marketing</a></h2>
			
			<div class="meta">
			
				<div class="authorinfo">
					March 3, 2015 by <a href="/user/1526576">Larisa Bedgood</a>
				</div>
				
				<div class="comment">
					<a href="http://smartdatacollective.com/lbedgood/302486/how-data-service-daas-revolutionizing-marketing#comments" title="comments"></a>
				</div>

                                
			</div>
	
			<div class="blurb-wrap">
				
								<div class="imageright">
					
					<a href="http://smartdatacollective.com/lbedgood/302486/how-data-service-daas-revolutionizing-marketing"><img src="http://smartdatacollective.com/sites/smartdatacollective.com/files/imagecache/featureLeft/Screen%20shot%202015-03-03%20at%202.24.18%20AM.png" alt="" title="" width="125" height="125" class="imagecache imagecache-featureLeft imagecache-default imagecache-featureLeft_default"/></a>
					
										<div class="attribution"><p><em>DaaS.</em></p></div>
										
				</div>
							
				<p>Rather than focusing on developing and managing an intricate network of data, companies can focus on the business outcomes and marketing advantages of Big Data. Generating immediate revenue from Big Data is a universal goal for most marketers - and DaaS makes this possible for businesses across any type of industry.<a href="/lbedgood/302486/how-data-service-daas-revolutionizing-marketing">[read more]</a></p>
				
